This project is licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License,
version 2.1 or (at your option) any later version (LGPL-2.1-or-later).

It links statically against FFmpeg (LGPL-2.1+, built from source via
vcpkg) and adapts code patterns from FFmpeg's fftools/ffplay.c, mpv's
audio/out/ao_wasapi.c, and VLC's subtitle/mmdevice modules (all
LGPL-2.1+). D3D11 VideoProcessor setup follows Microsoft's MIT-licensed
DX11VideoRenderer sample. No GPL components are used.

Full LGPL-2.1 text: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/lgpl-2.1.html
